title: "GH-448: boolean custom field is silently never persisted (data-loss class)"
description: "Dogfood GH-448: pm schema add-field --type boolean registers fine but values set via the derived flag are silently dropped on create/update — success reported, data lost. Duplicate check: searched boolean custom field — pm-vhbf/pm-qvdj (closed) shipped the field system; no open item covers the boolean coercion bug."
